original: Lindberg, Einar Harald, civilingenjör, Göteborg, f. 16/12/89 i Gbg av M. H. L. o. Maria Särnslröm. G. 18 m. Nanny Lundgren. Barn: Nils f. 19, repr., Birgit 21, Ingela 24. — Mog:ex. 08, civiling:ex. 11. Anst. v. Nya Fören. Elektr. A-B i Ludvika 12-16, STAL i Finspång 16-19, Elektr. A-B Eck i Partille 19-23, egen ing:firma 23-27, chef f. Sv. Elektromek. Ind. A-B filial i Gbg sed. 27.
translated: Lindberg, Einar Harald, civil engineer, Gothenburg, born on 16/12/89 in Gothenburg to M. H. L. and Maria Särnslröm. Married in 1918 to Nanny Lundgren. Children: Nils, born in 1919, representative; Birgit, born in 1921; Ingela, born in 1924. Obtained a master's degree in engineering in 1908 and a civil engineering degree in 1911. Employed by Nya Fören. Elektr. A-B in Ludvika from 1912 to 1916, STAL in Finspång from 1916 to 1919, Elektr. A-B Eck in Partille from 1919 to 1923, had his own engineering firm from 1923 to 1927, and became the head of the Swedish Elektromek. Ind. A-B branch in Gothenburg since 1927.
